'''Kongo ka Bɛjɛfanga Fasojamana''' (Franse: République démocratique du Congo) kuntaalasuruyala Kongo BF, kɔrɔlen a bɛ wele Kongo Yɛrɛta Dugu, Belgik Kongo, Kongo-Leopoldville, Kongo-Kinshasa ani Zayir ye jamana lafɛnsennen sabanan ye Afrika kɔnɔ. Alnayasɔrɔ a sigilen Cɛma Afrika Un dugumayɔrɔ, manto in ka sɔrɔko ani sigiyɔrɔ dabelen kataa Worodugu Afrika ma sabu a ye tɔnden ye [[Worodugu Afrika Yiriliwa Jɛkulu]] (SADC) la. A bɛ danbɔ ni [[Cɛma Afrika Fasojamana]] ye ani [[Sudan]] saheli fɛ, [[Uganda]], [[Rwanda]], ani [[Burundi]] kɔrɔn fɛ, [[Zanbia]] ani [[Angola]] worodugu fɛ, [[Kongo ka Fasojamana]] tlebi fɛ, a faralen kabɔ [[Tanzania]] la ni [[Dala Tankanika]] ye kɔrɔn fɛ.
